Route groups-
__________________

Use - (auth) in the folder name to have it removed from the url


Create a login folder-

Page.tsx -

export default function Login(){
    return(
        <>this is the login component</>
    )
}

Create a register folder -

Page.tsx-

export default function Register(){
    return(
        <>this is the Register component</>
    )
}

_____________

Move inside the auth folder-


We can access via - 

http://localhost:3000/auth/register

http://localhost:3000/auth/login


We need to add auth in routes


 To remove it add - (auth) in folder name and then we donâ€™t need to add In routes


